s', 'color': 'fef2c0', 'default': False, 'description': ''}], 'state': 'open', 'state_reason': None, 'locked': False, 'comments': 1, 'created_at': '2021-03-02T02:45:53Z', 'updated_at': '2022-07-15T02:10:44Z', 'author_association': 'CONTRIBUTOR', 'active_lock_reason': None, 'body': 'Howdy!\r\n\r\nIt\'s been a few months, some good, some bad, but all filled with great nextflow progress!\r\n\r\nI couldn\'t find a documented release schedule or process. Is this documented anywhere?\r\n\r\nEven if it\'s just "I release when I have time" - might be worth adding to the README. There\'s some unreleased features that would be helpful to have.\r\n\r\nI do know about the `-edge` releases. It\'s also not clear _how_ edge-y those are. Any guidance would be appreciated. If there\'s already words on this, feel free to point me at docs.', 'reactions': {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/nextflow-io/nextflow/discussions/1945/reactions', 'total_count': 0, '+1': 0, '-1': 0, 'laugh': 0, 'hooray': 0, 'confused': 0, 'heart': 0, 'rocket': 0, 'eyes': 0}, 'timeline_url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/nextflow-io/nextflow/discussions/1945/timeline'}, {'repository_url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/nextflow-io/nextflow', 'category': {'id': 32532274, 'node_id': 'MDE4OkRpc2N1c3Npb25DYXRlZ29yeTMyNTMyMjc0', 'repository_id': 9052236, 'emoji': ':pray:', 'name': 'Q&A', 'description': 'Ask the community for help', 'created_at': '2021-01-31T15:04:22.000Z', 'updated_at': '2021-01-31T15:04:22.000Z', 'slug': 'q-a', 'is_answerable': True}, 'answer_html_url': 'https://github.com/nextflow-io/nextflow/discussions/1949#discussioncomment-422920', 'answer_chosen_at': '2021-03-02T21:21:20.000Z', 'answer_chosen_by': {'login': 'jfxer', 'id': 24417395, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjI0NDE3Mzk1', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/24417395?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jfxer', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/jfxer', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jfxer/fo